      {
        "id": "how",
        "icon": "rocket_launch",
        "heading": {
          "en": "How do you start?",
          "zh": "怎麼開始用？"
        },
        "blocks": [
          {
            "type": "h3",
            "text": {
              "en": "Quick way: the REST API",
              "zh": "最快的方式：REST API"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "p",
            "text": {
              "en": "For one-off jobs you don't even need a Worker. Send a URL to an endpoint like /screenshot and get the result back. Other endpoints include /pdf, /content, /scrape, /snapshot, /json, /links and /markdown.",
              "zh": "處理一次性工作時，你連 Worker 都不用寫。把網址送到像 /screenshot 這樣的端點，就能拿回結果。其他端點還有 /pdf、/content、/scrape、/snapshot、/json、/links 和 /markdown。"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "lang": "bash",
            "title": {
              "en": "Screenshot via REST API",
              "zh": "用 REST API 截圖"
            },
            "body": "curl -X POST 'https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/accounts/{account_id}/browser-rendering/screenshot' \\\n  -H 'Authorization: Bearer {api_token}' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{ \"url\": \"https://example.com\" }' \\\n  --output screenshot.png"
          },
          {
            "type": "h3",
            "text": {
              "en": "Full control: Puppeteer in a Worker",
              "zh": "完全操控：在 Worker 裡用 Puppeteer"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "steps",
            "items": [
              {
                "title": {
                  "en": "Install the library",
                  "zh": "安裝函式庫"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Add Cloudflare's Puppeteer package to your Worker project.",
                  "zh": "把 Cloudflare 版的 Puppeteer 套件加進你的 Worker 專案。"
                },
                "code": {
                  "lang": "bash",
                  "body": "npm install @cloudflare/puppeteer"
                }
              },
              {
                "title": {
                  "en": "Add the browser binding",
                  "zh": "加上瀏覽器繫結"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Declare a browser binding in wrangler.jsonc so env.MYBROWSER is available in code.",
                  "zh": "在 wrangler.jsonc 宣告一個 browser 繫結，程式裡就能用 env.MYBROWSER。"
                },
                "code": {
                  "lang": "jsonc",
                  "body": "{\n  \"name\": \"my-browser-worker\",\n  \"main\": \"src/index.js\",\n  \"compatibility_date\": \"2025-06-01\",\n  \"browser\": {\n    \"binding\": \"MYBROWSER\"\n  }\n}"
                }
              },
              {
                "title": {
                  "en": "Drive the browser",
                  "zh": "操控瀏覽器"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Launch Chromium, open a page, go to a URL and screenshot it. Always close the browser when done to free resources.",
                  "zh": "啟動 Chromium、開一個分頁、前往網址並截圖。用完一定要關閉瀏覽器以釋放資源。"
                },
                "code": {
                  "lang": "js",
                  "body": "import puppeteer from \"@cloudflare/puppeteer\";\n\nexport default {\n  async fetch(request, env) {\n    const browser = await puppeteer.launch(env.MYBROWSER);\n    const page = await browser.newPage();\n    await page.goto(\"https://example.com\");\n    const image = await page.screenshot();\n    await browser.close();\n    return new Response(image, {\n      headers: { \"content-type\": \"image/png\" }\n    });\n  }\n};"
                }
              },
              {
                "title": {
                  "en": "Deploy",
                  "zh": "部署上線"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Publish your Worker and call it from anywhere.",
                  "zh": "把 Worker 發佈出去，就能從任何地方呼叫。"
                },
                "code": {
                  "lang": "bash",
                  "body": "wrangler deploy"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "concepts",
        "icon": "school",
        "heading": {
          "en": "Key concepts",
          "zh": "重點概念"
        },
        "blocks": [
          {
            "type": "cards",
            "items": [
              {
                "icon": "visibility_off",
                "title": {
                  "en": "Headless browser",
                  "zh": "無頭瀏覽器"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "A full browser running without a visible window — perfect for automation on a server.",
                  "zh": "一個沒有可見視窗、照常運作的完整瀏覽器——最適合在伺服器上做自動化。"
                }
              },
              {
                "icon": "integration_instructions",
                "title": {
                  "en": "Puppeteer & Playwright",
                  "zh": "Puppeteer 與 Playwright"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Popular libraries that let your code tell the browser what to click, type and capture.",
                  "zh": "熱門的函式庫，讓你的程式碼告訴瀏覽器要點什麼、輸入什麼、擷取什麼。"
                }
              },
              {
                "icon": "api",
                "title": {
                  "en": "REST API vs Bindings",
                  "zh": "REST API 對比繫結"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "REST endpoints are quick and code-free; bindings inside a Worker give full step-by-step control.",
                  "zh": "REST 端點快速又免寫程式；Worker 裡的繫結則能逐步完全操控。"
                }
              },
              {
                "icon": "sync",
                "title": {
                  "en": "Sessions",
                  "zh": "工作階段（Session）"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Reuse a warm browser across requests instead of launching a fresh one each time — faster and cheaper.",
                  "zh": "跨請求重用一個已暖機的瀏覽器，而不是每次都重開一個——更快也更省。"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "tips",
        "icon": "tips_and_updates",
        "heading": {
          "en": "Tips & limits",
          "zh": "小提示與限制"
        },
        "blocks": [
          {
            "type": "callout",
            "variant": "warn",
            "icon": "timer",
            "title": {
              "en": "Always close the browser",
              "zh": "記得關閉瀏覽器"
            },
            "text": {
              "en": "Call browser.close() (or reuse a session) when you're done. On the Free plan you get 10 minutes of browser time per day, so leaving browsers open wastes your quota.",
              "zh": "做完後請呼叫 browser.close()（或重用 session）。免費方案每天只有 10 分鐘的瀏覽器時間，讓瀏覽器一直開著會白白用掉額度。"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "ul",
            "items": {
              "en": [
                "Free plan: up to 3 concurrent browsers, a new one every 20 seconds, and 10 minutes total per day.",
                "Workers Paid plan: up to 120 concurrent browsers and a new one every second.",
                "Browsers idle out after 60 seconds by default (extendable up to 10 minutes).",
                "Reuse sessions to cut cold starts and stay within limits."
              ],
              "zh": [
                "免費方案：最多同時 3 個瀏覽器，每 20 秒可新開一個，每天合計 10 分鐘。",
                "Workers 付費方案：最多同時 120 個瀏覽器，每秒可新開一個。",
                "瀏覽器預設閒置 60 秒後關閉（可延長至 10 分鐘）。",
                "重用 session 可減少冷啟動，也比較不會撞到限制。"
              ]
            }
          }
        ]
      }
