      {
        "id": "how",
        "icon": "rocket_launch",
        "heading": {
          "en": "How to get started",
          "zh": "怎麼開始用？"
        },
        "blocks": [
          {
            "type": "p",
            "text": {
              "en": "We'll upload a video, wait for it to finish encoding, then embed the player. You only need an API token and your Account ID from the Cloudflare dashboard.",
              "zh": "我們會上傳一支影片、等它編碼完成，然後嵌入播放器。你只需要在 Cloudflare 控制台拿到一組 API 權杖和你的 Account ID。"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "steps",
            "items": [
              {
                "title": {
                  "en": "Set your credentials",
                  "zh": "設定憑證"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Export your API token and Account ID so the commands below can use them. The token is like a password for your code.",
                  "zh": "先把 API 權杖和 Account ID 設成環境變數，下面的指令才用得到。權杖就像給程式用的密碼。"
                },
                "code": {
                  "lang": "bash",
                  "body": "export CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=\"your-token-here\"\nexport ACCOUNT_ID=\"your-account-id-here\""
                }
              },
              {
                "title": {
                  "en": "Upload a video file",
                  "zh": "上傳影片檔"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "For files under 200 MB you can post the file directly. The -F file=@ part attaches a local video.",
                  "zh": "小於 200 MB 的檔案可以直接上傳，-F file=@ 就是附上本機影片檔。"
                },
                "code": {
                  "lang": "bash",
                  "body": "curl -X POST \\\n  https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/accounts/$ACCOUNT_ID/stream \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN\" \\\n  -F file=@/path/to/video.mp4"
                }
              },
              {
                "title": {
                  "en": "Or copy from a URL",
                  "zh": "或從網址匯入"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Already have the video online? Tell Stream to fetch it. The response includes a uid — the video's unique id.",
                  "zh": "影片已經在網路上了？直接叫 Stream 去抓。回應裡會有一個 uid，就是這支影片的唯一代號。"
                },
                "code": {
                  "lang": "bash",
                  "body": "curl -X POST \\\n  https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/accounts/$ACCOUNT_ID/stream/copy \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN\" \\\n  -d '{\"url\":\"https://example.com/video.mp4\",\"meta\":{\"name\":\"My first video\"}}'"
                }
              },
              {
                "title": {
                  "en": "Check it is ready",
                  "zh": "確認編碼完成"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Encoding takes a moment. When status.state is 'ready' and readyToStream is true, you can play it.",
                  "zh": "編碼需要一點時間。當 status.state 變成 ready、readyToStream 為 true，就可以播放了。"
                },
                "code": {
                  "lang": "json",
                  "body": "{\n  \"result\": {\n    \"uid\": \"6b9e68b07dfee8cc2d116e4c51d6a957\",\n    \"readyToStream\": true,\n    \"status\": { \"state\": \"ready\" }\n  },\n  \"success\": true\n}"
                }
              },
              {
                "title": {
                  "en": "Embed the player",
                  "zh": "嵌入播放器"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Paste this iframe into your page. Replace <CODE> with your customer code and <UID> with the video uid. Done — a full adaptive player appears.",
                  "zh": "把這段 iframe 貼到你的網頁，<CODE> 換成你的 customer code、<UID> 換成影片 uid。完成——一個完整的自適應播放器就出現了。"
                },
                "code": {
                  "lang": "html",
                  "body": "<iframe\n  src=\"https://customer-<CODE>.cloudflarestream.com/<UID>/iframe\"\n  title=\"My first video\"\n  allow=\"accelerometer; gyroscope; autoplay; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture;\"\n  allowfullscreen=\"true\"\n  style=\"border: none; width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16/9;\">\n</iframe>"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "callout",
            "variant": "note",
            "icon": "upload",
            "title": {
              "en": "Big files? Use tus",
              "zh": "大檔案？用 tus"
            },
            "text": {
              "en": "For uploads over 200 MB (up to a 30 GB max), Stream supports the tus protocol, which resumes the upload if your connection drops.",
              "zh": "超過 200 MB（最大 30 GB）的上傳，Stream 支援 tus 協定；它會在連線中斷時自動續傳，不用整個重來。"
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "concepts",
        "icon": "school",
        "heading": {
          "en": "Key concepts",
          "zh": "重點概念"
        },
        "blocks": [
          {
            "type": "cards",
            "items": [
              {
                "icon": "graphic_eq",
                "title": {
                  "en": "Adaptive bitrate 自適應位元率",
                  "zh": "Adaptive bitrate（自適應位元率）"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "The player automatically switches between quality levels based on the viewer's network — fewer buffering spinners.",
                  "zh": "播放器會依觀眾的網速自動切換畫質，減少「轉圈圈」卡頓。"
                }
              },
              {
                "icon": "sync_alt",
                "title": {
                  "en": "Transcoding 轉碼",
                  "zh": "Transcoding（轉碼）"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Converting your original into multiple resolutions and a streaming format (HLS/DASH). Stream does this for you.",
                  "zh": "把原始影片轉成多種解析度與串流格式（HLS／DASH）。這由 Stream 自動完成。"
                }
              },
              {
                "icon": "playlist_play",
                "title": {
                  "en": "HLS / DASH",
                  "zh": "HLS／DASH"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Streaming protocols that chop video into small chunks so playback can adapt quality on the fly.",
                  "zh": "串流協定，把影片切成小片段，讓播放時能即時切換畫質。"
                }
              },
              {
                "icon": "fingerprint",
                "title": {
                  "en": "Signed URLs 簽章網址",
                  "zh": "Signed URL（簽章網址）"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Time-limited tokens that restrict who can watch — perfect for paid or private content.",
                  "zh": "有時效的權杖，限制誰能觀看——很適合付費或私人內容。"
                }
              },
              {
                "icon": "drive_folder_upload",
                "title": {
                  "en": "Direct creator upload 直接上傳",
                  "zh": "Direct creator upload（直接上傳）"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "One-time upload URLs you give users so they upload to Stream without seeing your API token.",
                  "zh": "發給使用者的一次性上傳網址，讓他們直接上傳到 Stream，又看不到你的 API 權杖。"
                }
              },
              {
                "icon": "sensors",
                "title": {
                  "en": "Live input 直播輸入",
                  "zh": "Live input（直播輸入）"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "A reusable endpoint you stream to (via RTMPS/SRT) for live broadcasts, with optional recording.",
                  "zh": "一個可重複使用的端點，你用 RTMPS／SRT 推流上去做直播，還能選擇自動錄影。"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "tips",
        "icon": "tips_and_updates",
        "heading": {
          "en": "Tips & pricing",
          "zh": "小提示與計費"
        },
        "blocks": [
          {
            "type": "callout",
            "variant": "tip",
            "icon": "savings",
            "title": {
              "en": "How billing works",
              "zh": "計費方式"
            },
            "text": {
              "en": "You pay $5 per 1,000 minutes of video stored per month, and $1 per 1,000 minutes delivered (watched). Uploading and encoding are always free, and there are no separate bandwidth charges.",
              "zh": "每月每 1,000 分鐘「儲存」5 美元，每 1,000 分鐘「傳送（被觀看）」1 美元。上傳與編碼一律免費，也沒有額外的頻寬費。"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "callout",
            "variant": "warn",
            "icon": "inventory_2",
            "title": {
              "en": "Storage is prepaid",
              "zh": "儲存是預付制"
            },
            "text": {
              "en": "Stored minutes are bought in advance. If you run out, you can't upload new videos or start live streams until you add more storage or delete old videos.",
              "zh": "儲存分鐘數是預先購買的。一旦用完，在你加購或刪掉舊影片之前，就無法上傳新影片或開新直播。"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "ul",
            "items": {
              "en": [
                "Live and on-demand video are billed the same way — by minutes stored and delivered.",
                "Max single upload is 30 GB; use tus for anything large to get resumable uploads.",
                "Add captions/subtitles and a thumbnail to make videos more accessible and clickable.",
                "Use signed URLs for paid content so links can't be freely shared."
              ],
              "zh": [
                "直播與隨選影片計費方式相同——都看「儲存」與「傳送」的分鐘數。",
                "單檔上傳上限 30 GB；大檔請用 tus，才能斷線續傳。",
                "加上字幕與縮圖，讓影片更易讀也更吸引點擊。",
                "付費內容請用簽章網址，連結才不會被隨意轉傳。"
              ]
            }
          }
        ]
      }
