      {
        "id": "how",
        "icon": "rocket_launch",
        "heading": {
          "en": "How to turn it on",
          "zh": "怎麼開啟它"
        },
        "blocks": [
          {
            "type": "p",
            "text": {
              "en": "Most Smart Shield protections activate simply by routing your domain through Cloudflare. The key step is proxying your DNS records.",
              "zh": "大多數 Smart Shield 防護只要讓網域的流量經過 Cloudflare 就會啟用。關鍵步驟是把你的 DNS 紀錄設為代理。"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "steps",
            "items": [
              {
                "title": {
                  "en": "Proxy your DNS records",
                  "zh": "代理你的 DNS 紀錄"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "In DNS > Records, make sure your A/AAAA/CNAME records show the orange cloud. That single toggle routes traffic through Cloudflare and switches on the edge protections.",
                  "zh": "在 DNS > Records，確認 A／AAAA／CNAME 紀錄顯示橘色雲朵。這個開關會把流量導入 Cloudflare，並啟用邊緣防護。"
                }
              },
              {
                "title": {
                  "en": "Set SSL/TLS to a secure mode",
                  "zh": "把 SSL/TLS 設成安全模式"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Under SSL/TLS, choose Full (strict) so traffic is encrypted end to end between visitors, Cloudflare, and your origin.",
                  "zh": "在 SSL/TLS 裡選 Full (strict)（完整嚴格），讓訪客、Cloudflare 與來源伺服器之間全程加密。"
                }
              },
              {
                "title": {
                  "en": "Enable Always Use HTTPS",
                  "zh": "啟用 Always Use HTTPS"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Turn on 'Always Use HTTPS' so any http:// request is automatically upgraded to the secure https:// version.",
                  "zh": "開啟「Always Use HTTPS（一律使用 HTTPS）」，讓任何 http:// 請求自動升級成安全的 https:// 版本。"
                }
              },
              {
                "title": {
                  "en": "Confirm protection is active",
                  "zh": "確認防護已生效"
                },
                "text": {
                  "en": "Check the response headers — a 'server: cloudflare' header confirms your traffic is now flowing through and protected by the edge.",
                  "zh": "檢查回應標頭，看到「server: cloudflare」就代表流量已經穿過邊緣並受到保護。"
                },
                "code": {
                  "lang": "bash",
                  "body": "curl -sI https://example.com | grep -iE 'server|cf-ray'\n# server: cloudflare\n# cf-ray: 8a1b2c3d4e5f6789-LAX"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "tips",
        "icon": "tips_and_updates",
        "heading": {
          "en": "Tips & pricing",
          "zh": "小提示與計費"
        },
        "blocks": [
          {
            "type": "callout",
            "variant": "tip",
            "icon": "tune",
            "title": {
              "en": "Defaults first, then tune",
              "zh": "先用預設值，再來微調"
            },
            "text": {
              "en": "The automatic defaults are safe for almost everyone. Once you're comfortable, layer on WAF rules, finer cache rules, and Argo Smart Routing to go further.",
              "zh": "自動預設值對幾乎所有人都安全。等你上手後，再疊上 WAF 規則、更細的快取規則與 Argo 智慧路由，走得更遠。"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "ul",
            "items": {
              "en": [
                "Core protections like free SSL, default caching, and unmetered DDoS mitigation are available on the Free plan.",
                "Advanced pieces (like Argo Smart Routing or higher-tier WAF) are paid upgrades.",
                "Always pick Full (strict) SSL so the connection to your origin is also encrypted.",
                "Don't proxy mail records — keep MX and email-auth records DNS-only (grey cloud)."
              ],
              "zh": [
                "核心防護如免費 SSL、預設快取與不限量 DDoS 緩解，在免費方案就有。",
                "進階部分（如 Argo 智慧路由或更高階 WAF）是付費升級。",
                "務必選 Full (strict) SSL，連到來源伺服器的連線才會一起加密。",
                "別代理郵件相關紀錄，MX 與郵件驗證紀錄保持僅 DNS（灰色雲朵）。"
              ]
            }
          }
        ]
      }
