                "text": {
                  "en": "Files in public/ (HTML, CSS, JS, images) are cached and served from Cloudflare's edge worldwide.",
                  "zh": "public/ 裡的檔案（HTML、CSS、JS、圖片）會被快取，並從 Cloudflare 全球邊緣節點直接送出。"
                }
