        "en": "One Durable Object per room holds every open WebSocket and broadcasts messages to everyone; D1 keeps the history.",
        "zh": "每個房間用一個 Durable Object 握住所有開啟的 WebSocket 連線，把訊息廣播給所有人；D1 負責保存歷史紀錄。"
